类 EmptyObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • objects.EmptyObject
  • 直接已知子类:
    Loading, Map

    public abstract class EmptyObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class that will show the empty object on that be be handled by the handler
    作者:
    Leo
